		"description": "Complete API collection for Flask E-commerce Backend with JWT authentication and role-based access control.\n\n**Roles:**\n- Admin (full access)\n- Manager (manage products, categories, view orders)\n- Cashier (process orders, view today's orders)\n- Customer (shopping, cart, orders)\n\n**Base URL:** http://localhost:5000",
